00:06:27,670 --> 00:06:28,680
SOUMA.

39
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:07,520
Disappear, the light of hope that illuminates the darkness.

40
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:18,040
RYUGA, if you remain in this state, you will be consumed by evil.

41
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,250
RYUGA.

42
00:07:25,250 --> 00:07:26,660
Try turning darkness into light.

43
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:30,290
SENKOUKENBU and SENEIKENBU are two sides of the same coin.

44
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:36,610
You have overcome the trials of darkness, so you are sure to master it someday.

45
00:07:40,050 --> 00:07:44,930
I will transform all of GARO's golden light into the power of darkness.

46
00:08:16,900 --> 00:08:17,920
what?

47
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,620
Return to darkness.

48
00:09:08,310 --> 00:09:09,320
RYUGA.

49
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,340
SOUMA.

50
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,090
RYUGA slashed the HORROR.

51
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,560
RYUGA.

52
00:09:45,130 --> 00:09:46,910
You freed MUTSUGI from HORROR.

53
00:09:48,990 --> 00:09:50,010
thank you.

54
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:02,150
We now have to do something about the Gate of Destruction.

55
00:10:21,050 --> 00:10:26,240
The dragon's head held by the Gate of Destruction is a HORROR used by our ancestors to seal the gate.

56
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:30,410
It has awakened from a long slumber and is seeking the souls of people.

57
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,280
In that state, we can't get close to it.

58
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:38,020
SOUMA.

59
00:10:38,020 --> 00:10:39,030
There is a way.

60
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,460
It's a SENKOUKENBU.

61
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:53,810
I've never succeeded in that trick.

62
00:10:53,810 --> 00:10:57,440
GODOU believed that you could master the SENKOUKENBU.

63
00:10:59,170 --> 00:11:02,450
It is true that you were swallowed up by darkness that day.

64
00:11:03,970 --> 00:11:05,870
However, GODOU said:

65
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:11,460
It was impossible for SOUMA to do that.

66
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,330
No, it's the opposite.

67
00:11:19,130 --> 00:11:23,820
He heard my voice and came back from the darkness of his own free will.

68
00:11:26,340 --> 00:11:30,430
If he improves himself from now on, he will definitely be able to overcome the darkness.

69
00:11:36,260 --> 00:11:40,500
After all, SOUMA is a suitable successor to ZANGO.

70
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:46,820
Did my father say that?

71
00:11:49,490 --> 00:11:50,510
SOUMA.

72
00:11:52,740 --> 00:11:53,770
believe in yourself.

