84
00:13:20,210 --> 00:13:21,220
Okay.

85
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:09,510
SOUMA.

86
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:10,520
let's go.

87
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,530
Okay.

88
00:14:16,450 --> 00:14:17,980
Accept your own darkness.

89
